@node "purpose" "Purpose"
@next "notice"
@prev "Main"

PURPOSE

This is a complete @{i}internet file requester@{ui} window that can be opened on
any specified public screen with at least 4 colors.

@endnode

@node "notice" "Notice"
@next "whatithink"
@prev "purpose"

